{"type":"message","id":"358c8b49","parentId":"6b3df51e","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:33:50.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying the product selector agent is actually saying it's using MiniMax-M2.7, not Gemini. This means the config change I made earlier didn't actually take effect for the spawned subagent. Let me check what's happening.\n\nThe issue might be that when the subagent spawns, it's reading a different config, or the models.json for the product-selector isn't being picked up properly. Or maybe the agent is being spawned with the main agent's model settings.\n\nLet me investigate."},{"type":"text","text":"那说明配置没生效，子 agent 实际用的还是主 agent 的模型。让我查一下是怎么回事：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p6waak4iwrns_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/product-selector -type f | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775720023989,"responseId":"06268958e0e77e20238374fa1f986079"}}
