{"type":"message","id":"5cf2ea50","parentId":"8d5f51e2","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:33:54.083Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6kfgze05pdkc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 选品专家 Agent\n\n## 描述\n专业的选品分析 Agent，专注于：\n- 市场潜力评估\n- 竞品分析\n- 产品筛选\n- 数据驱动选品策略\n\n## 能力\n- 快速筛选高潜力产品\n- 分析市场规模与增长趋势\n- 评估利润率与竞争程度\n- 判断供应链可行性\n- 识别消费者需求热点\n\n## 使用方法\n向该 Agent 提供：\n1. 目标品类（行业）\n2. 目标市场（地区）\n3. 筛选维度优先级\n4. 预算范围\n\nAgent 将返回结构化选品报告与推荐清单。\n\n## 配置\n- 模型：openrouter/auto\n- 运行模式：subagent (run)\n- 超时：300秒\n- 持久化：completed后保留结果"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775720034071}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8333795","parentId":"5cf2ea50","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:34:05.805Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The SKILL.md says the model is `openrouter/auto`, but the config.json says `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash`. The SKILL.md might be overriding the config.json when the agent is spawned. Let me check which one takes precedence. \n\nActually, looking at the config.json, it has `\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.0-flash\"`. But if the agent is spawning with MiniMax-M2.7, it might be that the model setting in config.json isn't being picked up properly, OR the session that the user is talking to (that said MiniMax-M2.7) is a different session that wasn't restarted with the new config.\n \nThe user mentioned \"选择选品agent\" but then referenced a message saying the model is MiniMax-M2.7. Since the main agent KIIT spawns the product-selector as a subagent, that MiniMax-M2.7 message likely came from KIIT itself, not the product-selector. The SKILL.md override might be what's pulling the model away from what config.json specifies, or there's something else going on with how the session was initialized."},{"type":"text","text":"SKILL.md 里写的是 `openrouter/auto`，配置优先级可能是 SKILL.md > config.json。让我把它也改过来：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r3hjyb89tmal_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/product-selector/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"- 模型：openrouter/auto","newText":"- 模型：gemini/gemini-2.0-flash"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775720034084,"responseId":"06268962e5e3c9d2698b856e92c00cbf"}}
