{"type":"message","id":"e1889e56","parentId":"77a0974d","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:37:52.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue! Looking at the session:\n\n```json\n\"modelProvider\": \"openrouter\",\n\"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n\"authProfileOverride\": \"openrouter:default\",\n\"authProfileOverrideSource\": \"auto\",\n```\n\nThe session has an `authProfileOverride: \"openrouter:default\"` which is forcing it to use OpenRouter. This was set automatically by the system because... looking at the fallback notice:\n\n```json\n\"fallbackNoticeSelectedModel\": \"openrouter/auto\",\n\"fallbackNoticeActiveModel\": \"openrouter/free\",\n\"fallbackNoticeReason\": \"billing\"\n```\n\nThe reason is \"billing\" - it seems the system fell back to the free model because of billing issues with the configured model.\n \nSo the session-level override is the culprit—it's forcing OpenRouter despite the config changes, and the billing fallback reason suggests the system chose this provider because it was the free option available.\n\nI need to check the product-selector's auth-profiles.json to see what's actually configured there, since the sessions.json shows the override came from the auto source, but the auth-profiles file appears to be empty or has no profiles defined."},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了！看 sessions.json 里的关键字段：\n\n```json\n\"authProfileOverride\": \"openrouter:default\",\n\"authProfileOverrideSource\": \"auto\",\n```\n\n系统自动把模型覆盖成了 OpenRouter，原因是 **billing** —— 配置的模型欠费或无法访问，自动降级到了免费模型。\n\n而且 authProfiles 是空的 `{}`，说明从来没有配置过选品 Agent 的认证信息。\n\n问题可能是 gemini key 绑定的计费账户有问题，或者需要单独为 product-selector 配置 authProfile。我来给它单独建一个：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q8xuhnmbmg52_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/product-selector/auth-profiles.json","content":"{\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"profiles\": {\n    \"gemini:default\": {\n      \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n      \"model\": \"gemini-2.0-flash\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"AIzaSyDLi65k75qE_76nMM-i2aPhzHLUmKKZK7Y\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775720255106,"responseId":"06268a3fabffe0771acfbada2d0e098f"}}
