{"type":"message","id":"cb024344","parentId":"c062fc60","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:38:05.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the sessions.json to use this auth profile instead of \"openrouter:default\". The session is already failed though. But the authProfileOverride was set to \"openrouter:default\" from \"auto\" source. \n\nActually, the real problem might be that when the subagent runs, it picks up openrouter:default from somewhere. The `authProfileOverrideSource: \"auto\"` suggests it was auto-assigned.\n\nActually, the session is for the conversation with the user. The authProfile override is on the session itself, not on the agent. So each new conversation/session might get a different override.\n\nLet me think about where the `authProfileOverrideSource: \"auto\"` comes from. \n\nThis is likely a default behavior when spawning a subagent. When you spawn a subagent, if no explicit auth profile is set, it uses the default one from the agent's auth-profiles.json. But the current session (the user's chat with the product-selector agent) has the override set to \"openrouter:default\", which means it's being routed through OpenRouter's free model instead.\n\nThe real issue is that OpenRouter is triggering billing controls—likely because the API key is empty or exhausted—so when it tries to use the configured model, it falls back to openrouter/free. I should force the auth profile to gemini:default to bypass this."},{"type":"text","text":"现在更新 sessions.json，把这个会话的 authProfileOverride 改成 gemini：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kbkhvu012ru1_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/product-selector/sessions/sessions.json","edits":[{"oldText":"\"authProfileOverride\": \"openrouter:default\",\n    \"authProfileOverrideSource\": \"auto\",","newText":"\"authProfileOverride\": \"gemini:default\",\n    \"authProfileOverrideSource\": \"manual\","}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775720272260,"responseId":"06268a5001dcfb66578b9698bc0687c1"}}
