{"type":"message","id":"63551ff0","parentId":"0a9bc1e8","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:44:42.795Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So product-selector is not in the agents list. I need to add it. Let me look at what a proper agent entry looks like and add a product-selector entry.\n\nActually, wait - the `product-selector` is defined as a subagent in `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/product-selector/`. But it's not registered in `openclaw.json`'s `agents.list`. \n\nThe issue is that subagents spawned via `sessions_spawn` with `runtime: \"subagent\"` and `mode: \"run\"` might be using the `agents.defaults.subagents.model` config which is `gemini/gemini-1.5-flash`.\n \nSo I have two options: either add `product-selector` to the `agents.list` with the gemini model, or modify the `subagents.model` setting directly. Looking at the current config, the subagent model is already set to `gemini/gemini-1.5-flash`, which is probably why it's not picking up the model I configured. I need to either change that default or explicitly override it when spawning.\n\nActually, I should add `product-selector` to the agents list as a separate entry since it has its own workspace and configuration directory. Let me examine the main agent config more closely to understand the proper structure for adding it."},{"type":"text","text":"确认了，product-selector 没有在 `openclaw.json` 的 agents 列表里，所以它走的是 subagent 默认配置（`gemini/gemini-1.5-flash`）。需要把它加进去：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1o311gin3l6d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nagents = d.get('agents', {})\nagent_list = agents.get('list', [])\nfor a in agent_list:\n    print(json.dumps(a, indent=2)[:500])\n    print('---')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775735071452,"responseId":"0626c41fec55bedf0a087d90823258f9"}}
