{"type":"message","id":"d2e81fa2","parentId":"d233bc12","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:48:03.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying TTS agent is the \"product-selector\" agent, and asking me to rename it so I can recognize it better. Let me check the current config - the tts agent is named \"TTS-选品专家\" which literally means \"TTS-Product Selection Expert\". So TTS IS the product selector! And it uses `gemini/gemini-1.5-flash`.\n\nThe user wants me to rename the agent in the config so I can tell them apart, and also change its model to gemini-2.0-flash."},{"type":"text","text":"TTS 就是选品 Agent 啊！它叫 `TTS-选品专家`，难怪我一直没认出来。我来把它改名为\"选品 Agent\"，模型也顺便换成 `gemini-2.0-flash`：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c9baiwrhcgc3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\n\nfor agent in d['agents']['list']:\n    if agent['id'] == 'tts':\n        print('Before:', json.dumps(agent, ensure_ascii=False))\n        agent['id'] = 'selector'\n        agent['name'] = '选品专家'\n        agent['model'] = 'gemini/gemini-2.0-flash'\n        print('After:', json.dumps(agent, ensure_ascii=False))\n\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\nprint('Saved.')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775735263459,"responseId":"0626c4dffd1f0694974a8adc0141027c"}}
