{"type":"message","id":"1afbf5f2","parentId":"39995c95","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:56:42.761Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ta6acpfsjraq_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This image shows a screenshot of a status update from an AI chat interface or bot platform, likely within a messaging app like Telegram. It displays the current configuration and resource status of the AI models being used.\n\nHere is a detailed breakdown of the information presented:\n\n### **Top Header and Context**\n*   **Timestamp:** The time \"19:55\" is visible at the top left.\n*   **Avatar:** A small profile icon of a red, cartoonish monster with large teeth is shown.\n*   **User Interaction:** The text next to the avatar says **\"回复 HALEI: 现在在检查一下模型\"**, which translates to \"Reply to HALEI: Checking the model now.\"\n*   **Main Header:** Below the reply is the primary status heading: **\"当前模型: MiniMax-M2.7\"** (Current model: MiniMax-M2.7).\n\n### **Information Table**\nA table with two columns, **\"项目\" (Item)** and **\"值\" (Value)**, provides the following details:\n\n1.  **当前模型 (Current Model):**\n    *   **Value:** `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`\n    *   This indicates the primary active Large Language Model (LLM).\n\n2.  **默认备用模型 (Default Fallback Model):**\n    *   **Value:** `gemini/gemini-1.5-flash`\n    *   This indicates the model the system will switch to if the primary MiniMax model fails.\n\n3.  **Token余额 (Token Balance):**\n    *   **Value:** `5小时剩余约87%` (Approx. 87% remaining for 5 hours).\n    *   This is a status indicator for usage limits or remaining credits.\n\n4.  **推理模式 (Inference Mode / Reasoning Mode):**\n    *   **Value:** `关闭 (Think: off)` (Closed/Off (Think: off)).\n    *   This indicates that a specific reasoning or deep-thinking mode for the AI is currently disabled.\n\n### **Status Indicators and Footer**\n*   **Status/Completion:** At the bottom, it says **\"已完成\"** (Completed).\n*   **Execution Time:** Next to the