{"type":"message","id":"499c3c61","parentId":"d5070b50","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:58:04.172Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the problem clearly:\n\n1. The tts agent's `agent/config.json` doesn't exist (empty output, exit code 1)\n2. The tts agent's `models.json` has a `gemini` provider but it only has `gemini-1.5-flash`, NOT `gemini-2.0-flash`!\n\nSo even though we set `model: gemini/gemini-2.0-flash` in openclaw.json for the tts agent, the models.json for tts only has `gemini-1.5-flash` registered. When it tries to use `gemini-2.0-flash`, it can't find it in the models list, so it falls back to defaults.\n \nThe fix is straightforward—I need to add `gemini-2.0-flash` to the tts agent's models.json file under the gemini provider."},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了！tts 的 `models.json` 里有 gemini provider，但**只有 `gemini-1.5-flash`**，没有 `gemini-2.0-flash`。所以虽然 openclaw.json 里配了 `gemini-2.0-flash`，但这个模型在 tts 的 models.json 里根本不存在。\n\n补上 `gemini-2.0-flash`：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0lydcumj24c2_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/models.json","edits":[{"oldText":"\"id\": \"gemini-1.5-flash\",\n          \"name\": \"gemini-1.5-flash\",\n          \"api\": \"google-generative-ai\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\n            \"text\"\n          ],\n          \"cost\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 0,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0\n          },\n          \"contextWindow\": 200000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        }\n      ]","newText":"\"id\": \"gemini-1.5-flash\",\n          \"name\": \"gemini-1.5-flash\",\n          \"api\": \"google-generative-ai\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\n            \"text\"\n          ],\n          \"cost\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 0,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0\n