{"type":"message","id":"f3b6356c","parentId":"3ff5a966","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:01:22.179Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3lwci152ugvw_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the image provided, here is a detailed description of the models and configuration values shown in the interface for the agent named \"**选品专家**\" (Selection Expert):\n\n### **1. Top-Level Configuration Metadata**\nShown in the \"Overview\" section under \"Workspace paths and identity metadata\":\n\n*   **Workspace:** `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-selector`\n*   **Primary Model (Summary Display):** `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash`\n*   **Skills Filter:** `all skills`\n\n---\n\n### **2. Model Selection Settings**\nThese are the specific settings configured for the agent's behavior:\n\n*   **Primary model:** The dropdown is set to **\"Inherit default (minimax/MiniMax-M2.7)\"**.\n    *   *Note: There appears to be a discrepancy between the summary display at the top (which says Gemini 2.0 Flash) and this dropdown setting (which indicates it is inheriting a Minimax M2.7 default).*\n*   **Fallbacks:** This section lists backup models to use if the primary model fails.\n    *   **Fallback Model 1:** `gemini/gemini-1.5-flash`\n\n---\n\n### **3. Interface Context**\n*   **Current Agent:** 选品专家 (Selection Expert).\n*   **Current Tab:** Overview. Other available tabs include Files (8), Tools, Skills, Channels (3), and Cron Jobs.\n*   **UI Language:** The sidebar and main headings are in Chinese, while specific technical values and model names are in English.\n*   **Sidebar Navigation:** The user is currently in the \"代理\" (Agent) section under \"控制\" (Control). Other sidebar options include \"聊天\" (Chat), \"技能\" (Skills), \"节点\" (Nodes), \"梦境\" (Dreamscape), and various \"设置\" (Settings) like \"配置\" (Configuration) and \"自动化\" (Automation).\n*   **Actions:** At the bottom of the \"Overview\" pane, there are buttons for **\"重新加载配置\"** (Reload Configuration) and **\"Save\"**. In the top right, there are options for **\"Copy ID\"** and **\"Set Default\"**."}],"details":{"model":"minimax/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/3e743cb9-1f04-4e68-b49d-7b978185e481.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775736082160}}
{"type":"message","id":"69450804","parentId":"f3b6356c","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:01:32.297Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The image shows the UI for the 选品专家 agent. Key findings:\n\n1. Primary Model shows \"Inherit default (minimax/MiniMax-M2.7)\" in the dropdown\n2. But the Summary shows `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash`\n3. Fallback: `gemini/gemini-1.5-flash`\n\nSo the issue is that the dropdown says \"Inherit default\" which means it's using the global default (MiniMax-M2.7), not the model we set in the agent config.\n\nThe model dropdown in the UI shows \"Inherit default (minimax/MiniMax-M2.7)\" - this means the UI is showing that the primary model is set to inherit from the global defaults, not explicitly set to gemini-2.0-flash.\n\n\nI need to check what we actually wrote to the openclaw.json file to see if our configuration changes were properly applied or if the UI is overriding our settings."},{"type":"text","text":"看到了，UI 里 Primary Model 显示的是 **\"Inherit default (minimax/MiniMax-M2.7)\"**——说明虽然 openclaw.json 里配了 `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash`，但 UI 显示它仍在继承全局默认值。\n\n让我确认一下 openclaw.json 里 tts 的配置是否真的写进去了：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s8ocn34mfp5a_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\nfor agent in d['agents']['list']:\n    if agent['id'] == 'tts':\n        print(json.dumps(agent, indent=2))\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775736082182,"responseId":"0626c812b3001729947eb3e0a132294a"}}
