{"type":"message","id":"21b5be44","parentId":"0a3f4571","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:02:00.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tts agent doesn't have an `agent/config.json` file! That's the problem. When the agent is loaded, it looks for `agent/config.json` inside the agentDir, but that file doesn't exist. So the model setting in openclaw.json's `agents.list[].model` might be separate from the actual agent's config file.\n\nWait, but openclaw.json has `agentDir: /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent`. And there's no `agent/config.json` inside that directory. The agentDir points to a directory that doesn't have a config.json!\n\nActually, looking at the main agent structure:\n\n\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/` has an `agent/config.json`\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/` has `auth-profiles.json` and `models.json` but NO `config.json`\n\nSo the tts agent is missing its `config.json` file entirely, which could be why the model configuration isn't being picked up properly."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4yhgkii6bpf0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775736107614,"responseId":"0626c82b2b9b38fff31f90d5c272d42c"}}
