{"type":"message","id":"e3d8ce59","parentId":"8f4f2105","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:08:41.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that the UI shows the correct config now, but when they actually ask the agent, it's still using the wrong model. This means the running agent isn't picking up the new config. Let me check the current sessions for tts to see what model it's actually using, and also check if there's a cached session that's holding onto the old model.\n\nLet me look at the tts sessions."},{"type":"text","text":"UI 配置对了，但实际调用时模型还是错的。让我查一下 tts 当前的 session 状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5zakpur1nbsw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/sessions.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nfor k, v in d.items():\n    print('Session:', k[:80])\n    print('  model:', v.get('model','?'))\n    print('  authProfileOverride:', v.get('authProfileOverride','?'))\n    print('  status:', v.get('status','?'))\n    print()\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775736510778,"responseId":"0626c9bf183355b5fde906ae79c5d9e6"}}
