{"type":"message","id":"ed30bc74","parentId":"288711d5","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:23:01.185Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4s4fx25nabie_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The image is a screenshot of a chat interface displaying a conversation in Chinese about an AI assistant's settings.\n\n### Models and Versions\nThe following model names and versions are explicitly mentioned:\n*   **MiniMax-M2.7**: Identified as the \"currently running model\" (当前运行模型).\n*   **Gemini 2.0 Flash**: Identified as the \"default model\" (默认模型).\n\n### Configuration Values and Context\n*   **Assistant Persona**: The AI introduces itself as a \"product selection expert\" (选品专家) specializing in hair accessories for TikTok Shop sites in Thailand and Vietnam.\n*   **Target User**: The messages are addressed to a user named \"HALEI.\"\n\n### Status Indicators\n*   **Completion Status**: The last message includes a status indicator at the bottom: \"Completed · Time taken 5.8s\" (已完成 · 耗时 5.8s).\n*   **Command Usage**: The conversation begins with a command `/new`, which appears to have reset the session or started a new task."}],"details":{"model":"minimax/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/10117996-2115-49f9-82b1-8c9337868de3.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775737381169}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c8058c3","parentId":"ed30bc74","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:23:12.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the TTS selector agent says:\n- 当前运行模型: MiniMax-M2.7 (the model actually being used right now)\n- 默认模型: Gemini 2.0 Flash (the default model configured)\n\nThis confirms that despite all our config changes, the actual running model is still MiniMax-M2.7. The default/fallback model is gemini-2.0-flash but it's not being used as the primary.\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. The authProfile is set to \"gemini:default\" but the model showing is still MiniMax-M2.7. This suggests the model selection isn't coming from the authProfileOverride alone.\n \nI'm realizing the system might be configured with MiniMax as the primary model at a higher priority level, with gemini-2.0-flash as a fallback—so even though the account is set to use gemini, the system is still preferring MiniMax for actual runs. I'm realizing the TTS agent's config.json is separate from the global openclaw.json settings, so even though I set `model: \"gemini/gemini-2.0-flash\"` in the agent config, it might not be overriding the global defaults if the system is reading from a different configuration source or respecting global precedence rules."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_33yton073e6n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/sessions.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nfor k, v in d.items():\n    print(json.dumps(v, indent=2))\n\" 2>/dev/null | head -60"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775737381187,"responseId":"0626cd25a79a60df78d74bc51260c07d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ba5ed4c","parentId":"9c8058c3","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:23:12.403Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_33yton073e6n_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionId\": \"70b63536-33a5-4e33-a22c-784825ed287f\",\n  \"updatedAt\": 1775737308653,\n  \"systemSent\": true,\n  \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n  \"modelOverride\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n  \"providerOverride\": \"minimax\",\n  \"chatType\": \"direct\",\n  \"deliveryContext\": {\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"to\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n    \"accountId\": \"tts\"\n  },\n  \"lastChannel\": \"feishu\",\n  \"lastTo\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"lastAccountId\": \"tts\",\n  \"origin\": {\n    \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n    \"provider\": \"feishu\",\n    \"surface\": \"feishu\",\n    \"chatType\": \"direct\",\n    \"from\": \"feishu:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n    \"to\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n    \"accountId\": \"tts\"\n  },\n  \"sessionFile\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/70b63536-33a5-4e33-a22c-784825ed287f.jsonl\",\n  \"compactionCount\": 0,\n  \"skillsSnapshot\": {\n    \"prompt\": \"\\n\\nThe following skills provide specialized instructions for specific tasks.\\nUse the read tool to load a skill's file when the task matches its description.\\nWhen a skill file references a relative path, resolve it against the skill directory (parent of SKILL.md / dirname of the path) and use that absolute path in tool commands.\\n\\n<available_skills>\\n  <skill>\\n    <name>feishu-bitable</name>\\n    <description>\\u98de\\u4e66\\u591a\\u7ef4\\u8868\\u683c\\uff08Bitable\\uff09\\u7684\\u521b\\u5efa\\u3001\\u67e5\\u8be2\\u3001\\u7f16\\u8f91\\u548c\\u7ba1\\u7406\\u5de5\\u5177\\u3002\\u5305\\u542b 27 \\u79cd\\u5b57\\u6bb5\\u7c7b\\u578b\\u652f\\u6301\\u3001\\u9ad8\\u7ea7\\u7b5b\\u9009\\u3001\\u6279\\u91cf\\u64cd\\u4f5c\\u548c\\u89c6