{"type":"message","id":"30e2e77c","parentId":"e86dc07c","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:56:46.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the logs, I can see the key issue:\n\n```\n\"feishu[kiit][msg:om_x100b524e402f30a4c4473b95eb605f7]: reply mode resolved (effectiveReplyMode=static, replyMode=static, chatType=p2p)\"\n```\n\nAnd then:\n```\n\"feishu[kiit][msg:om_x100b524e402f30a4c4473b95eb605f7]: footer config resolved (accountId=kiit, sessionKey=agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb, chatType=p2p, useStreamingCards=false, rawFooter={\\\"elapsed\\\":false,\\\"status\\\":false}, resolvedFooter={\\\"status\\\":false,\\\"elapsed\\\":false,\\\"tokens\\\":false,\\\"cache\\\":false,\\\"context\\\":false,\\\"model\\\":false})\"\n\n\n```\n\nYet despite the streaming cards being disabled, the typing indicator is still being added to the message. This suggests the typing indicator might be controlled by a separate mechanism from the streaming cards configuration.\n\nLooking at the typing callbacks in the reply dispatcher, even when streaming is disabled, the typing indicator gets triggered. The footer configuration and streaming card logic both correctly show false, but there's no parameter to globally disable the typing indicator itself.\n\n```\nreply mode resolved (effectiveReplyMode=static, replyMode=static, chatType=p2p)\n```\nSo the reply mode IS correctly static, but the typing indicator still runs. There's no skipTyping parameter at the top level of the Feishu config schema.\n\nI'm confused about what the user is actually reporting - they said they turned off the \"思考中\" thinking indicator, but I disabled streaming. The footer showed \"thinking...\" but I'm not sure if that's the same thing they're referring to.\n\nLet me re-read what they said about it showing as a yellow piano icon on their phone with \"思考中\" text. That sounds like the typing indicator, not the footer text. But in the latest message they said \"不行，还是有提示\" - still showing. So my streaming fix didn't address what they're actually complaining about."},{"type":"text","text":"日志显示配置是正确的（`effectiveReplyMode=static`，`useStreamingCards=false`），但 typing indicator（打字提示）还是被添加了。这个 typing indicator 是通过飞书 emoji reaction 实现的，不是 streaming 卡本身控制的。\n\n需要找飞书插件里有没有单独的开关：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ild7g10c9qbx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"skipTyping\\|disableTyping\\|typingIndicator\\|typing.*disable\\|disable.*typing\" /home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/src/card/reply-dispatcher.js 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775739392323,"responseId":"0626d500a08793e4c7387f62d3ff9ea9"}}
